{
  "video_id": "PeZ-U0pj9LI",
  "title": "Thomas Insel: Toward a new understanding of mental illness",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Thu-Huong Ha"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12530.0,
      "end_time": 15491.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s start with some good news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15491.0,
      "end_time": 17840.0,
      "text": "and the good news has to do with what do we know"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 17840.0,
      "end_time": 20107.0,
      "text": "based on biomedical research"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20107.0,
      "end_time": 23561.0,
      "text": "that actually has changed the outcomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23561.0,
      "end_time": 26660.0,
      "text": "for many very serious diseases?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26660.0,
      "end_time": 28907.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start with leukemia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28907.0,
      "end_time": 31435.0,
      "text": "acute lymphoblastic leukemia, ALL,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31435.0,
      "end_time": 33873.0,
      "text": "the most common cancer of children."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33873.0,
      "end_time": 35835.0,
      "text": "When I was a student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35835.0,
      "end_time": 39675.0,
      "text": "the mortality rate was about 95 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39675.0,
      "end_time": 42808.0,
      "text": "Today, some 25, 30 years later, we&#39;re talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42808.0,
      "end_time": 46435.0,
      "text": "a mortality rate that&#39;s reduced by 85 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46435.0,
      "end_time": 49510.0,
      "text": "Six thousand children each year"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49510.0,
      "end_time": 53240.0,
      "text": "who would have previously died of this disease are cured."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53240.0,
      "end_time": 55310.0,
      "text": "If you want the really big numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55310.0,
      "end_time": 57859.0,
      "text": "look at these numbers for heart disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57859.0,
      "end_time": 59651.0,
      "text": "Heart disease used to be the biggest killer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59651.0,
      "end_time": 61155.0,
      "text": "particularly for men in their 40s."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61155.0,
      "end_time": 64649.0,
      "text": "Today, we&#39;ve seen a 63-percent reduction in mortality"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64649.0,
      "end_time": 66710.0,
      "text": "from heart disease --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66710.0,
      "end_time": 71595.0,
      "text": "remarkably, 1.1 million deaths averted every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71595.0,
      "end_time": 74316.0,
      "text": "AIDS, incredibly, has just been named,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74316.0,
      "end_time": 76597.0,
      "text": "in the past month, a chronic disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76597.0,
      "end_time": 79512.0,
      "text": "meaning that a 20-year-old who becomes infected with HIV"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79512.0,
      "end_time": 83583.0,
      "text": "is expected not to live weeks, months, or a couple of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83583.0,
      "end_time": 85853.0,
      "text": "as we said only a decade ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85853.0,
      "end_time": 88244.0,
      "text": "but is thought to live decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88245.0,
      "end_time": 92741.0,
      "text": "probably to die in his &#39;60s or &#39;70s from other causes altogether."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92741.0,
      "end_time": 95766.0,
      "text": "These are just remarkable, remarkable changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95766.0,
      "end_time": 98355.0,
      "text": "in the outlook for some of the biggest killers."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98355.0,
      "end_time": 100434.0,
      "text": "And one in particular"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100434.0,
      "end_time": 102479.0,
      "text": "that you probably wouldn&#39;t know about, stroke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102479.0,
      "end_time": 104800.0,
      "text": "which has been, along with heart disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104800.0,
      "end_time": 106258.0,
      "text": "one of the biggest killers in this country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106258.0,
      "end_time": 108480.0,
      "text": "is a disease in which now we know"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108490.0,
      "end_time": 110978.0,
      "text": "that if you can get people into the emergency room"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 110978.0,
      "end_time": 113152.0,
      "text": "within three hours of the onset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113152.0,
      "end_time": 115757.0,
      "text": "some 30 percent of them will be able to leave the hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115757.0,
      "end_time": 118876.0,
      "text": "without any disability whatsoever."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 118876.0,
      "end_time": 121133.0,
      "text": "Remarkable stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121133.0,
      "end_time": 123164.0,
      "text": "good-news stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123164.0,
      "end_time": 126229.0,
      "text": "all of which boil down to understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126229.0,
      "end_time": 129580.0,
      "text": "something about the diseases that has allowed us"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129580.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132904.0,
      "text": "to detect early and intervene early."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 132904.0,
      "end_time": 135390.0,
      "text": "Early detection, early intervention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 135390.0,
      "end_time": 138108.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the story for these successes."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138109.0,
      "end_time": 140845.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the news is not all good."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140845.0,
      "end_time": 143194.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s talk about one other story"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143194.0,
      "end_time": 144885.0,
      "text": "which has to do with suicide."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144885.0,
      "end_time": 147536.0,
      "text": "Now this is, of course, not a disease, per se."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 147537.0,
      "end_time": 150625.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a condition, or it&#39;s a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 150625.0,
      "end_time": 152414.0,
      "text": "that leads to mortality."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152414.0,
      "end_time": 155494.0,
      "text": "What you may not realize is just how prevalent it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 155494.0,
      "end_time": 159703.0,
      "text": "There are 38,000 suicides each year in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159703.0,
      "end_time": 162461.0,
      "text": "That means one about every 15 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 162461.0,
      "end_time": 165237.0,
      "text": "Third most common cause of death amongst people"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165237.0,
      "end_time": 168130.0,
      "text": "between the ages of 15 and 25."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 168130.0,
      "end_time": 170261.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of an extraordinary story when you realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 170261.0,
      "end_time": 172773.0,
      "text": "that this is twice as common as homicide"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 172773.0,
      "end_time": 175422.0,
      "text": "and actually more common as a source of death"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 175422.0,
      "end_time": 178757.0,
      "text": "than traffic fatalities in this country."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 178757.0,
      "end_time": 181389.0,
      "text": "Now, when we talk about suicide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 181389.0,
      "end_time": 184501.0,
      "text": "there is also a medical contribution here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 184501.0,
      "end_time": 186933.0,
      "text": "because 90 percent of suicides"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186933.0,
      "end_time": 188703.0,
      "text": "are related to a mental illness:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 188703.0,
      "end_time": 191749.0,
      "text": "depression, bipolar disorder, schizophrenia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 191749.0,
      "end_time": 194807.0,
      "text": "anorexia, borderline personality. There&#39;s a long list"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 194808.0,
      "end_time": 196917.0,
      "text": "of disorders that contribute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 196917.0,
      "end_time": 200941.0,
      "text": "and as I mentioned before, often early in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 200941.0,
      "end_time": 204145.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not just the mortality from these disorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 204145.0,
      "end_time": 205787.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also morbidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 205787.0,
      "end_time": 208480.0,
      "text": "If you look at disability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208480.0,
      "end_time": 210200.0,
      "text": "as measured by the World Health Organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210200.0,
      "end_time": 213725.0,
      "text": "with something they call the Disability Adjusted Life Years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 213725.0,
      "end_time": 215821.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s kind of a metric that nobody would think of"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 215821.0,
      "end_time": 217135.0,
      "text": "except an economist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 217135.0,
      "end_time": 220577.0,
      "text": "except it&#39;s one way of trying to capture what is lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 220577.0,
      "end_time": 223760.0,
      "text": "in terms of disability from medical causes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223760.0,
      "end_time": 226653.0,
      "text": "and as you can see, virtually 30 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 226653.0,
      "end_time": 228917.0,
      "text": "of all disability from all medical causes"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228917.0,
      "end_time": 231477.0,
      "text": "can be attributed to mental disorders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 231477.0,
      "end_time": 233861.0,
      "text": "neuropsychiatric syndromes."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 233861.0,
      "end_time": 236120.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re probably thinking that doesn&#39;t make any sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 236130.0,
      "end_time": 238685.0,
      "text": "I mean, cancer seems far more serious."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 238685.0,
      "end_time": 241717.0,
      "text": "Heart disease seems far more serious."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241717.0,
      "end_time": 244757.0,
      "text": "But you can see actually they are further down this list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 244757.0,
      "end_time": 247370.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s because we&#39;re talking here about disability."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 247370.0,
      "end_time": 249829.0,
      "text": "What drives the disability for these disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249829.0,
      "end_time": 253733.0,
      "text": "like schizophrenia and bipolar and depression?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 253733.0,
      "end_time": 256708.0,
      "text": "Why are they number one here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 256708.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258217.00000000003,
      "text": "Well, there are probably three reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 258216.0,
      "end_time": 260188.0,
      "text": "One is that they&#39;re highly prevalent."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 260189.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263484.0,
      "text": "About one in five people will suffer from one of these disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 263484.0,
      "end_time": 266610.0,
      "text": "in the course of their lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 266610.0,
      "end_time": 268381.0,
      "text": "A second, of course, is that, for some people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 268381.0,
      "end_time": 269965.0,
      "text": "these become truly disabling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 269965.0,
      "end_time": 273920.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s about four to five percent, perhaps one in 20."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 273930.0,
      "end_time": 277357.0,
      "text": "But what really drives these numbers, this high morbidity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 277357.0,
      "end_time": 279786.0,
      "text": "and to some extent the high mortality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 279786.0,
      "end_time": 283734.0,
      "text": "is the fact that these start very early in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 283734.0,
      "end_time": 286829.0,
      "text": "Fifty percent will have onset by age 14,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 286829.0,
      "end_time": 289949.0,
      "text": "75 percent by age 24,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 289949.0,
      "end_time": 293414.0,
      "text": "a picture that is very different than what one would see"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 293414.0,
      "end_time": 295685.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re talking about cancer or heart disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 295685.0,
      "end_time": 299850.0,
      "text": "diabetes, hypertension -- most of the major illnesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 299850.0,
      "end_time": 303181.0,
      "text": "that we think about as being sources of morbidity and mortality."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 303181.0,
      "end_time": 309491.0,
      "text": "These are, indeed, the chronic disorders of young people."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 309491.0,
      "end_time": 312358.0,
      "text": "Now, I started by telling you that there were some good-news stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 312358.0,
      "end_time": 313806.0,
      "text": "This is obviously not one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 313806.0,
      "end_time": 316685.0,
      "text": "This is the part of it that is perhaps most difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 316685.0,
      "end_time": 319269.0,
      "text": "and in a sense this is a kind of confession for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 319269.0,
      "end_time": 324621.0,
      "text": "My job is to actually make sure that we make progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 324621.0,
      "end_time": 326972.0,
      "text": "on all of these disorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 326973.0,
      "end_time": 328683.0,
      "text": "I work for the federal government."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 328683.0,
      "end_time": 330700.0,
      "text": "Actually, I work for you. You pay my salary."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 330701.0,
      "end_time": 333850.0,
      "text": "And maybe at this point, when you know what I do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 333850.0,
      "end_time": 335205.0,
      "text": "or maybe what I&#39;ve failed to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 335205.0,
      "end_time": 337414.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll think that I probably ought to be fired,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 337414.0,
      "end_time": 339568.0,
      "text": "and I could certainly understand that."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 339569.0,
      "end_time": 341901.0,
      "text": "But what I want to suggest, and the reason I&#39;m here"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 341901.0,
      "end_time": 345156.0,
      "text": "is to tell you that I think we&#39;re about to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 345156.0,
      "end_time": 349819.0,
      "text": "in a very different world as we think about these illnesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 349819.0,
      "end_time": 352925.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;ve been talking to you about so far is mental disorders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 352925.0,
      "end_time": 354641.0,
      "text": "diseases of the mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 354641.0,
      "end_time": 358370.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s actually becoming a rather unpopular term these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 358370.0,
      "end_time": 360236.0,
      "text": "and people feel that, for whatever reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 360237.0,
      "end_time": 363614.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s politically better to use the term behavioral disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 363614.0,
      "end_time": 367525.0,
      "text": "and to talk about these as disorders of behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 367525.0,
      "end_time": 369792.0,
      "text": "Fair enough. They are disorders of behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 369792.0,
      "end_time": 371792.0,
      "text": "and they are disorders of the mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 371792.0,
      "end_time": 374196.0,
      "text": "But what I want to suggest to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 374197.0,
      "end_time": 375949.0,
      "text": "is that both of those terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 375949.0,
      "end_time": 378967.0,
      "text": "which have been in play for a century or more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 378967.0,
      "end_time": 381787.0,
      "text": "are actually now impediments to progress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 381787.0,
      "end_time": 386116.0,
      "text": "that what we need conceptually to make progress here"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 386117.0,
      "end_time": 391325.0,
      "text": "is to rethink these disorders as brain disorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 391325.0,
      "end_time": 393187.0,
      "text": "Now, for some of you, you&#39;re going to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 393187.0,
      "end_time": 395406.0,
      "text": "\"Oh my goodness, here we go again."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 395406.0,
      "end_time": 398340.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to hear about a biochemical imbalance"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 398340.0,
      "end_time": 399769.0,
      "text": "or we&#39;re going to hear about drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 399769.0,
      "end_time": 404595.0,
      "text": "or we&#39;re going to hear about some very simplistic notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 404595.0,
      "end_time": 407535.0,
      "text": "that will take our subjective experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 407535.0,
      "end_time": 413607.0,
      "text": "and turn it into molecules, or maybe into some sort of"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 413607.0,
      "end_time": 416825.0,
      "text": "very flat, unidimensional understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 416825.0,
      "end_time": 420926.0,
      "text": "of what it is to have depression or schizophrenia."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 420927.0,
      "end_time": 425425.0,
      "text": "When we talk about the brain, it is anything but"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 425425.0,
      "end_time": 428688.0,
      "text": "unidimensional or simplistic or reductionistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 428688.0,
      "end_time": 431647.0,
      "text": "It depends, of course, on what scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 431647.0,
      "end_time": 433943.0,
      "text": "or what scope you want to think about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 433943.0,
      "end_time": 440222.0,
      "text": "but this is an organ of surreal complexity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 440223.0,
      "end_time": 443694.0,
      "text": "and we are just beginning to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 443694.0,
      "end_time": 445867.0,
      "text": "how to even study it, whether you&#39;re thinking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 445867.0,
      "end_time": 448449.0,
      "text": "the 100 billion neurons that are in the cortex"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 448449.0,
      "end_time": 450594.0,
      "text": "or the 100 trillion synapses"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 450594.0,
      "end_time": 452953.0,
      "text": "that make up all the connections."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 452953.0,
      "end_time": 456529.0,
      "text": "We have just begun to try to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 456529.0,
      "end_time": 460570.0,
      "text": "how do we take this very complex machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 460570.0,
      "end_time": 462801.0,
      "text": "that does extraordinary kinds of information processing"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 462801.0,
      "end_time": 465518.0,
      "text": "and use our own minds to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 465518.0,
      "end_time": 469490.0,
      "text": "this very complex brain that supports our own minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 469490.0,
      "end_time": 471609.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually a kind of cruel trick of evolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 471609.0,
      "end_time": 475438.0,
      "text": "that we simply don&#39;t have a brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 475439.0,
      "end_time": 478337.0,
      "text": "that seems to be wired well enough to understand itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 478337.0,
      "end_time": 480651.0,
      "text": "In a sense, it actually makes you feel that"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 480651.0,
      "end_time": 483489.0,
      "text": "when you&#39;re in the safe zone of studying behavior or cognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 483489.0,
      "end_time": 484811.0,
      "text": "something you can observe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 484812.0,
      "end_time": 487817.0,
      "text": "that in a way feels more simplistic and reductionistic"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 487817.0,
      "end_time": 492785.0,
      "text": "than trying to engage this very complex, mysterious organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 492785.0,
      "end_time": 495213.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re beginning to try to understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 495213.0,
      "end_time": 498869.0,
      "text": "Now, already in the case of the brain disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 498869.0,
      "end_time": 500597.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;ve been talking to you about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 500597.0,
      "end_time": 502870.0,
      "text": "depression, obsessive compulsive disorder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 502870.0,
      "end_time": 505320.0,
      "text": "post-traumatic stress disorder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 505320.0,
      "end_time": 507974.0,
      "text": "while we don&#39;t have an in-depth understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 507974.0,
      "end_time": 511700.0,
      "text": "of how they are abnormally processed"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 511700.0,
      "end_time": 513804.0,
      "text": "or what the brain is doing in these illnesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 513804.0,
      "end_time": 516859.0,
      "text": "we have been able to already identify"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 516860.0,
      "end_time": 519436.0,
      "text": "some of the connectional differences, or some of the ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 519436.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521940.00000000006,
      "text": "in which the circuitry is different"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 521940.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523756.00000000006,
      "text": "for people who have these disorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 523756.0,
      "end_time": 525514.0,
      "text": "We call this the human connectome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 525514.0,
      "end_time": 527895.0,
      "text": "and you can think about the connectome"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 527895.0,
      "end_time": 529766.0,
      "text": "sort of as the wiring diagram of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 529767.0,
      "end_time": 531871.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll hear more about this in a few minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 531871.0,
      "end_time": 534822.0,
      "text": "The important piece here is that as you begin to look"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 534822.0,
      "end_time": 538799.0,
      "text": "at people who have these disorders, the one in five of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 538799.0,
      "end_time": 540627.0,
      "text": "who struggle in some way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 540627.0,
      "end_time": 542915.0,
      "text": "you find that there&#39;s a lot of variation"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 542915.0,
      "end_time": 546131.0,
      "text": "in the way that the brain is wired,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 546131.0,
      "end_time": 548733.0,
      "text": "but there are some predictable patterns, and those patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 548733.0,
      "end_time": 552546.0,
      "text": "are risk factors for developing one of these disorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 552547.0,
      "end_time": 555539.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a little different than the way we think about brain disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 555539.0,
      "end_time": 558307.0,
      "text": "like Huntington&#39;s or Parkinson&#39;s or Alzheimer&#39;s disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 558307.0,
      "end_time": 560699.0,
      "text": "where you have a bombed-out part of your cortex."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 560699.0,
      "end_time": 563959.0,
      "text": "Here we&#39;re talking about traffic jams, or sometimes detours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 563959.0,
      "end_time": 566705.0,
      "text": "or sometimes problems with just the way that things are connected"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 566706.0,
      "end_time": 567953.0,
      "text": "and the way that the brain functions."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 567953.0,
      "end_time": 571122.0,
      "text": "You could, if you want, compare this to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 571123.0,
      "end_time": 574172.0,
      "text": "on the one hand, a myocardial infarction, a heart attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 574172.0,
      "end_time": 575995.0,
      "text": "where you have dead tissue in the heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 575995.0,
      "end_time": 579592.0,
      "text": "versus an arrhythmia, where the organ simply isn&#39;t functioning"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 579592.0,
      "end_time": 581843.0,
      "text": "because of the communication problems within it."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 581843.0,
      "end_time": 583812.0,
      "text": "Either one would kill you; in only one of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 583812.0,
      "end_time": 586412.0,
      "text": "will you find a major lesion."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 586412.0,
      "end_time": 589244.0,
      "text": "As we think about this, probably it&#39;s better to actually go"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 589244.0,
      "end_time": 592467.0,
      "text": "a little deeper into one particular disorder, and that would be schizophrenia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 592467.0,
      "end_time": 594603.0,
      "text": "because I think that&#39;s a good case"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 594603.0,
      "end_time": 598127.0,
      "text": "for helping to understand why thinking of this as a brain disorder matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 598128.0,
      "end_time": 602600.0,
      "text": "These are scans from Judy Rapoport and her colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 602600.0,
      "end_time": 604178.0,
      "text": "at the National Institute of Mental Health"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 604178.0,
      "end_time": 607894.0,
      "text": "in which they studied children with very early onset schizophrenia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 607894.0,
      "end_time": 609364.0,
      "text": "and you can see already in the top"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 609364.0,
      "end_time": 611901.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s areas that are red or orange, yellow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 611901.0,
      "end_time": 614390.0,
      "text": "are places where there&#39;s less gray matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 614390.0,
      "end_time": 615577.0,
      "text": "and as they followed them over five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 615577.0,
      "end_time": 617815.0,
      "text": "comparing them to age match controls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 617815.0,
      "end_time": 619637.0,
      "text": "you can see that, particularly in areas like"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 619637.0,
      "end_time": 621953.0,
      "text": "the dorsolateral prefrontal cortex"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 621953.0,
      "end_time": 626283.0,
      "text": "or the superior temporal gyrus, there&#39;s a profound loss of gray matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 626283.0,
      "end_time": 627826.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s important, if you try to model this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 627826.0,
      "end_time": 629782.0,
      "text": "you can think about normal development"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 629782.0,
      "end_time": 633350.0,
      "text": "as a loss of cortical mass, loss of cortical gray matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 633350.0,
      "end_time": 636699.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s happening in schizophrenia is that you overshoot that mark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 636699.0,
      "end_time": 638267.0,
      "text": "and at some point, when you overshoot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 638268.0,
      "end_time": 641259.0,
      "text": "you cross a threshold, and it&#39;s that threshold"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 641259.0,
      "end_time": 644835.0,
      "text": "where we say, this is a person who has this disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 644835.0,
      "end_time": 647123.0,
      "text": "because they have the behavioral symptoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 647123.0,
      "end_time": 649244.0,
      "text": "of hallucinations and delusions."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 649244.0,
      "end_time": 650721.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s something we can observe."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 650721.0,
      "end_time": 656363.0,
      "text": "But look at this closely and you can see that actually they&#39;ve crossed a different threshold."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 656363.0,
      "end_time": 659359.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve crossed a brain threshold much earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 659359.0,
      "end_time": 662499.0,
      "text": "that perhaps not at age 22 or 20,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 662499.0,
      "end_time": 665267.0,
      "text": "but even by age 15 or 16 you can begin to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 665267.0,
      "end_time": 667627.0,
      "text": "the trajectory for development is quite different"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 667627.0,
      "end_time": 671141.0,
      "text": "at the level of the brain, not at the level of behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 671142.0,
      "end_time": 673237.0,
      "text": "Why does this matter? Well first because,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 673237.0,
      "end_time": 676379.0,
      "text": "for brain disorders, behavior is the last thing to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 676379.0,
      "end_time": 679289.0,
      "text": "We know that for Alzheimer&#39;s, for Parkinson&#39;s, for Huntington&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 679289.0,
      "end_time": 681723.0,
      "text": "There are changes in the brain a decade or more"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 681723.0,
      "end_time": 686762.0,
      "text": "before you see the first signs of a behavioral change."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 686763.0,
      "end_time": 689707.0,
      "text": "The tools that we have now allow us to detect"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 689707.0,
      "end_time": 694400.0,
      "text": "these brain changes much earlier, long before the symptoms emerge."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 694400.0,
      "end_time": 697403.0,
      "text": "But most important, go back to where we started."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 697403.0,
      "end_time": 700619.0,
      "text": "The good-news stories in medicine"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 700619.0,
      "end_time": 703563.0,
      "text": "are early detection, early intervention."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 703563.0,
      "end_time": 707227.0,
      "text": "If we waited until the heart attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 707227.0,
      "end_time": 711202.0,
      "text": "we would be sacrificing 1.1 million lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 711202.0,
      "end_time": 713611.0,
      "text": "every year in this country to heart disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 713611.0,
      "end_time": 716190.0,
      "text": "That is precisely what we do today"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 716190.0,
      "end_time": 720531.0,
      "text": "when we decide that everybody with one of these brain disorders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 720531.0,
      "end_time": 723733.0,
      "text": "brain circuit disorders, has a behavioral disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 723733.0,
      "end_time": 726957.0,
      "text": "We wait until the behavior becomes manifest."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 726957.0,
      "end_time": 731516.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not early detection. That&#39;s not early intervention."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 731516.0,
      "end_time": 733320.0,
      "text": "Now to be clear, we&#39;re not quite ready to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 733321.0,
      "end_time": 736475.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have all the facts. We don&#39;t actually even know"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 736475.0,
      "end_time": 739240.0,
      "text": "what the tools will be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 739240.0,
      "end_time": 743283.0,
      "text": "nor what to precisely look for in every case to be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 743283.0,
      "end_time": 747488.0,
      "text": "to get there before the behavior emerges as different."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 747488.0,
      "end_time": 750425.0,
      "text": "But this tells us how we need to think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 750425.0,
      "end_time": 751914.0,
      "text": "and where we need to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 751914.0,
      "end_time": 753116.0,
      "text": "Are we going to be there soon?"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 753116.0,
      "end_time": 755794.0,
      "text": "I think that this is something that will happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 755794.0,
      "end_time": 758625.0,
      "text": "over the course of the next few years, but I&#39;d like to finish"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 758625.0,
      "end_time": 761160.0,
      "text": "with a quote about trying to predict how this will happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 761160.0,
      "end_time": 763521.0,
      "text": "by somebody who&#39;s thought a lot about changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 763521.0,
      "end_time": 765848.0,
      "text": "in concepts and changes in technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 765849.0,
      "end_time": 768113.0,
